snippet.title: Pop Fix Podcast
snippet.description:
The Pop Fix Podcast is your weekly hit of Pop culture news, gossip and reality TV craziness.  The podcast is available on all Podcasts apps and Spotify and is hosted by Marni, Katy and Sama

The show is produced by Piccolo Podcasts

Producers: Emmeline Peterson & Andrew Menczel
